======== SAMPLE 1 ========
 I am writing this letter to you with open and genuine sorrow my sorrow and sorrowpity cognate to the following: my dear beloved sister, my dear son, and I extend this letter in the spirit of hope and the utmost valour which I have ever richly deservedly hoped for in myself and my beloved wife Abacha. I know that you shall suffer immense sorrow and expense hereafter, but I believe that by the grace of the Almighty you will be rich and powerful and will begrudge me everything that is not immediately compensation. I know that you will suffer enormous sorrow and expense hereafter, but I believe that by the grace of the Almighty you will be rich and will begrudge me everything that is not immediately compensation.

